Citation.sTitle: Kinematic Viscosities for Ether + Alkane Mixtures: Experimental Results and UNIFAC-VISCO Parameters
Citation.sAbstract: Kinematic viscosities for the binary mixtures of diisopropylether, dibutylether, or methyl ter-butyl ether with 3-methylpentane, hexane, or heptane have been measured at 283.15 K, 298.15 K, and 313.15 K. The experimental values have been correlated by the McAllister equation. Using these results, new UNIFAC-VISCO parameters, Oether-CH2 and Oether-CH3, have been calculated.
